data.description: Spacious 4 bedrooms/3 bathroom home with a brand new roof installed December 2018, a split floor plan that includes a fireplace, formal dining room, vaulted ceilings and a screened-in patio with hot tub.  Large kitchen with a breakfast bar, new stainless steel refrigerator, stove, microwave, and dishwasher. A cozy breakfast nook.  The master bathroom features a shower, garden tub, double vanity, and 2 walk-in closets.  Beautiful fenced in back yard with more patio area and a storage shed.
data.whatILove: Just 10 miles from NAS Pensacola with an open floor plan, screened porch and fully fenced back yard!  Located conveniently near shopping, dining, and close to interstate!  Only 20 min to Downtown Pensacola and 25 min to Pensacola Beach!  Navy Federal Heritage Oaks campus is only 10 min away!
